1
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:42,600
It's just ahead.

2
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:43,280
The Tian residence.

3
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:44,640
The deceased is the head of the Tian family,

4
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:45,160
Tian Wan.

5
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,480
Mother is here.

6
00:00:57,360 --> 00:00:57,640
Don't be afraid.

7
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,280
You are the deceased's wife?

8
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:06,040
Yes.

9
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:08,080
I am Lady Tian,

10
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:09,320
Chen Lian.

11
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:13,080
I see your two daughters

12
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,840
are both of marriageable age.

13
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:16,880
These children's toys are...

14
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,240
My husband once took a Concubine.

15
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:21,040
She was expecting to give birth,

16
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:22,680
and the whole family was overjoyed.

17
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:25,400
We prepared the swaddling clothes and necessities early.

18
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:28,080
But alas, the Concubine died suddenly from bleeding.

19
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:29,520
My husband was grief-stricken,

20
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,680
so he kept these items.

21
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:32,880
Just to...

22
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,800
keep them as a memento.

23
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,520
Where is the deceased?

24
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,680
In the room.

25
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:45,520
Let's go in and take a look.

26
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,800
I fear the cause of death matches Hu Pin's.

27
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,000
Guiyi.

28
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,280
Have someone take the body back.

29
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:28,920
Perform an autopsy.

30
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:29,680
Yes.

31
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,200
Did you find anything?

32
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,120
There are no signs of forced entry.

33
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:41,200
Inside the room,

34
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:42,800
there was no robbery,

35
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,520
nor any traces of a struggle.

36
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:46,960
Who do you think it could be?

37
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:53,640
Mother.

38
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,720
I'm scared.

39
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:55,680
Mother.

40
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,240
I'm scared too.

41
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:58,920
It's all right.

42
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,240
Mother is here.

43
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,400
Did anyone else visit the residence tonight?

44
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:15,080
My husband just returned from a business trip today.

45
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,840
He retired early to rest.

46
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,800
I also took the two children to sleep in the east room.

47
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,280
We didn't hear anyone come.

48
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,720
Was the deceased acquainted with Hu Pin from East Street?

49
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,320
I do not know him,

50
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,760
nor have I heard my husband mention that name.

51
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,440
You ask about this person, my lord...

52
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,880
is he related to my husband's death?

53
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:41,640
Could you take us to see the Concubine's room?

54
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,160
The cause of death is exactly the same as Hu Pin's.

55
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,040
Both were stabbed deeply by a sharp weapon.

56
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,080
Both killed by a single fatal blow.

57
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,600
If it was Chen Lian,

58
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,120
then what is her relationship with Hu Pin?

59
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:54,960
Could it be...

60
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,680
it was that concubine?

61
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,440
That concubine.

62
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,160
There isn't much dust in the room.

63
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,720
Obviously, it hasn't been vacant for long.

64
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,120
If what Chen Lian said is true,

65
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,720
the room wouldn't be this clean.

66
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,640
Feather dusters, small bells, sachets!

67
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:10,920
Come and take a look!

68
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:12,760
Feather dusters, small bells, sachets!

69
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:13,200
Gossipmonger.

70
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,000
Come and take a look.

71
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:19,120
Isn't this the lady who bought my goods last time?

72
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,320
And... and this is...

73
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,320
Does Tian Wan have a concubine?

74
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:24,520
Yes.

75
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,080
No.

76
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,440
Yes or no?

77
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,000
Be straight with me.

78
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,840
A woman did move into Tian Wan's house before.

79
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:33,600
But...

80
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:34,920
she wasn't a concubine.

81
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,480
What do you mean?

82
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,200
Regarding taking a concubine,

83
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,280
Tian Wan has complained many times.

84
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:45,280
Feather dusters, small bells, sachets!

85
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,280
Come buy some!

86
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,880
Do you think the problem is me,

87
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:49,880
or is the land no good?

88
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,120
I think the land is no good.

89
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,160
Then get a new piece of land.

90
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,120
Isn't this Brother Tian?

91
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,520
What's the matter?

92
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,000
Why the long face?

93
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:58,920
Shoo, shoo.

94
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,800
What else could it be?

95
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:04,040
He wants a Young Master.

96
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,200
That Chen Lian can't bear a son.

97
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,400
And she won't let him take a concubine.

98
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,960
Look at how she beat him this time.

99
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,920
That woman is too vicious.

100
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,200
You, go stand aside.

101
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,720
You have no idea.

102
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,400
That Chen Lian's temper...

103
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,000
she is a tigress.

104
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,160
Extremely fierce.

105
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,320
If Tian Wan dared to take a concubine,

106
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,680
Chen Lian would break his legs.

107
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,040
Really?

108
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:26,680
Really.

109
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,920
The information you buy from me,

110
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,600
Lady, you can rest assured.

111
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:33,760
Chen Lian bore Tian Wan two girls.

112
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,800
If you were Tian Wan,

113
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,360
wouldn't you want to find a woman

114
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:38,600
to have a Young Master

115
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,840
to continue the family line?

116
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,000
Filthy mouth.

117
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:43,400
It's the truth.

118
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:44,880
Then let me ask you,

119
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:47,400
what is this woman's background?

120
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,440
Lady, this money...

121
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,520
I'd better return it to you.

122
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,720
I really don't know.

123
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,040
Go ask someone else.

124
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:56,720
Feather dusters, small bells!

125
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:16,960
Lady Chen Lian.

126
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,520
In such a rush,

127
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:19,880
where are you going?

128
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,760
I have some things to ask you.

129
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,720
I hope you will answer truthfully.

130
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:27,280
Guiyi.

131
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:28,960
Look after the two children.

132
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:32,960
Please rest assured, My Lady.

133
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,000
If the children suffer the slightest harm,

134
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,040
I will pay with my life.

135
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:37,240
Mother.

136
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,480
Let's go, go play with your sister for a while.

137
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,360
Aren't you going out?

138
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:00,960
Why didn't you extinguish the brazier?

139
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,160
Aren't you afraid of a fire?

140
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,520
I was careless.
